My meme

meme1 <- image_read("https://pic.baike.soso.com/ugc/baikepic2/20444/cut-20180818231215-1211854547_jpg_629_419_24943.jpg/1284")
image_scale1 <- image_scale(meme1,400)
meme2 <- image_read("https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQRorFf_WqmhN7yevPJXPMmZMEpibDSluYa2Q&usqp=CAU")

image_scale2 <- image_scale(meme2,400)

blank1 <- image_blank(width = 400,
            height = 400, 
            color = "#953500") %>%
  image_annotate(text = "witchcraft",
                 color = "#999999",
                 size = 40,
                 font = "center")

blank2 <- image_blank(width = 400,
                      height = 400, 
                      color = "#596628") %>%
  image_annotate(text = "Be afraid,human",
                 color = "#999999",
                 size = 40,
                 font = "center")

picture <- c(blank1,image_scale1,image_scale2,blank2)

final_image <-image_append(picture)

final_image

animation <- image_animate(picture,fps = 1)

image_write(animation,"my_animation.gif")
